---
---

<section id="tentang" class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden border-t border-slate-50 scroll-mt-20 md:scroll-mt-28">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">

    <!-- Section Header (Konsisten dengan section lain) -->
    <div class="mb-10 md:mb-16 text-left">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-indigo-50 px-3 py-1.5 md:px-4 md:py-2 rounded-full border border-indigo-100 mb-4 md:mb-6">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 md:w-2 md:h-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-600 animate-pulse"></span>
        <span class="text-[11px] md:text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-700 leading-none">Tentang Kami</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tight uppercase leading-tight">
        Ruang <span class="text-indigo-600 italic font-serif font-light lowercase tracking-normal">alternatif</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-3 md:mt-4 text-slate-500 font-medium max-w-xl text-sm md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Mengenal lebih dekat perjalanan, gagasan, dan arah gerak Komunitas Literasi Brebesan.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Content Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-start">
      
      <!-- Kolom Kiri: Narasi & Visi Misi (Span 7) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8 md:space-y-10">
        
        <div class="prose prose-slate prose-sm md:prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
            Komunitas Literasi Brebes (Literasi Brebesan) adalah sebuah kolektif independen yang bergerak di bidang literasi dan kebudayaan. Kami percaya bahwa literasi bukan sekadar kemampuan membaca dan menulis, melainkan alat untuk membedah realitas dan merawat nalar kritis.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
            Berdiri di Kabupaten Brebes, kami berupaya menciptakan ruang-ruang diskusi yang inklusif bagi siapa saja yang ingin bertumbuh dan bergerak bersama melalui aksi nyata.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Visi & Misi Card -->
        <div id="visi-misi" class="bg-slate-50 rounded-[2rem] p-6 md:p-8 border border-slate-100 space-y-6 md:space-y-8 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-indigo-900/5 transition-all duration-500 relative overflow-hidden">
          
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-8 -mt-8 w-32 h-32 bg-indigo-500/5 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>

          <div class="relative z-10 space-y-3 md:space-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-black text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-tight flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"/></svg>
              </span>
              Visi
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed pl-11">
              Mewujudkan masyarakat Brebes yang literat, kritis, dan berdaya melalui penguatan budaya literasi alternatif.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="h-px bg-slate-200/60 w-full relative z-10"></div>

          <div class="relative z-10 space-y-4 md:space-y-5">
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-black text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-tight flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
              </span>
              Misi
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 md:space-y-4 list-none p-0 m-0 pl-11">
              {[
                "Menyediakan ruang diskusi dan belajar bersama yang terbuka.",
                "Menginisiasi gerakan membaca dan menulis di akar rumput.",
                "Berkolaborasi dengan berbagai pihak untuk aksi sosial budaya.",
                "Mendokumentasikan narasi dan gagasan lokal melalui publikasi."
              ].map(item => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-600 font-medium text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                  {item}
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Kolom Kanan: Sejarah (Span 5) -->
      <div id="sejarah" class="lg:col-span-5 relative">
        <div class="sticky top-24 lg:top-32 space-y-6 md:space-y-8 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 md:p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-indigo-900/5 transition-all duration-500">
          
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-black text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-tight flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 md:mb-8">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </span>
            Jejak Langkah
          </h3>
          
          <div class="relative pl-6 md:pl-8 border-l-2 border-slate-100 space-y-8 md:space-y-12">
            <!-- Timeline Item 1 -->
            <div class="relative group cursor-default">
              <div class="absolute -left-[33px] md:-left-[41px] top-0 w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-600 border-4 border-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-indigo-100 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-indigo-500"></div>
              <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-indigo-600 block mb-1 md:mb-2 leading-none transition-colors">2023</span>
              <h4 class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1.5 md:mb-2 group-hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">Awal Perjumpaan</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                Bermula dari kegelisahan beberapa pemuda akan minimnya ruang diskusi alternatif di Brebes. Diskusi kecil mulai rutin diadakan di berbagai ruang publik.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Timeline Item 2 -->
            <div class="relative group cursor-default">
              <div class="absolute -left-[33px] md:-left-[41px] top-0 w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 rounded-full bg-slate-200 border-4 border-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-100 transition-all group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-indigo-600 group-hover:ring-indigo-100"></div>
              <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-slate-300 block mb-1 md:mb-2 leading-none group-hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">2024</span>
              <h4 class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1.5 md:mb-2 group-hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">Penguatan Kolektif</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                Mulai merapikan struktur kolektif dan meluncurkan berbagai program rutin seperti Lapak Baca Gratis dan Diskusi Mingguan.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Timeline Item 3 -->
            <div class="relative group cursor-default">
              <div class="absolute -left-[33px] md:-left-[41px] top-0 w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 rounded-full bg-slate-200 border-4 border-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-100 transition-all group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-indigo-600 group-hover:ring-indigo-100"></div>
              <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-slate-300 block mb-1 md:mb-2 leading-none group-hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">2025</span>
              <h4 class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1.5 md:mb-2 group-hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">Ekspansi Gerakan</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                Mengintegrasikan teknologi informasi melalui website untuk mendokumentasikan tulisan dan gagasan kawan-kawan komunitas secara lebih luas.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 md:pt-8 border-t border-slate-100">
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium italic text-slate-500 relative pl-4 border-l-2 border-indigo-200">
              "Literasi bukan tentang seberapa banyak buku yang kau lahap, tapi tentang seberapa jernih kau melihat dunia setelahnya."
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
